        -:   15:/***Computing principal curvatures and directions by estimating per-vertex shape operators
        -:   16: Based on "Smooth Feature Lines on Surface Meshes" by Hildebrandt et al. 2005
        -:   17: Input:
        -:   18: V:          matrix |V|x3 of vertices
        -:   19: F:          matrix of vertex indices indicating faces
        -:   20: EV:         |E|x2 of edges (vertex indices)
        -:   21: EF:         |E|x2 left and right faces of each edge (-1 where boundary).
        -:   22: faceNormals:        |F|x3 normalized face normals
        -:   23: vertexNormals:      |V|x3 normalized vertex normals
        -:   24: Output:
        -:   25: Se:         vector of 3x3 shape operators per edge
        -:   26: Sf:           the same for vertices
        -:   27: Sv:         the same for vertices
        -:   28: ***/
